{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "11.0",
      "line_index": 11,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8fae9875",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "夜も深まり、宇宙船の展望デッキには二人だけ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "13.0",
      "line_index": 13,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "91c82c7e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "窓の向こうには無数の星が広がり、{G_PlayerName}はその光をぼんやりと眺めていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c6e02565",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その少し後ろでは、コハルが何かを思いついたように笑っている。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.1",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ae8d187a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ねぇ、ゲームしない？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "25.0",
      "line_index": 25,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3fe2a034",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "どんなゲームだよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.1",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "64ade61",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "今から十分間、あんたを照れさせたら、あたしの勝ち",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "31.0",
      "line_index": 31,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6898fdb2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "絶対やだ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.1",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ba3f7c80",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "拒否権なし。もう始まってるから♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.0",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7f0bc988",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは{G_PlayerName}の正面へ回り込み、その顔をじっと覗き込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.0",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "91e01c99",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "まっすぐに向けられた視線に耐えきれず、{G_PlayerName}は思わず顔を逸らしてしまった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "51.1",
      "line_index": 51,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2a8c508e",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "はい、一点",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.0",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e6a45f0e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "まだ何もしてないだろ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "57.1",
      "line_index": 57,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "78a9f8ee",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "目、逸らした。言い訳は聞きませーん♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.0",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "46bd6dcf",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そんなのありかよ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.0",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8f89daea",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "楽しそうに笑うコハルは、さらに{G_PlayerName}との距離を縮めていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.1",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d799e783",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ほら、動かないで",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "70.0",
      "line_index": 70,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a3131741",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "今度は何だよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "76.0",
      "line_index": 76,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ac69e3a3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは乱れていた{G_PlayerName}の襟元へ指先を伸ばし、丁寧に形を整えていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "533b0753",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その手が胸元に触れそうになり、{G_PlayerName}は慌てて身体を後ろへ引いた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.0",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "87b2dba0",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "じ、自分でやるから！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "86.1",
      "line_index": 86,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "80f72b8d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "はい、二点。顔、赤くなってる",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f45df985",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ち、違う！　……赤い星の光のせいだ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "92.1",
      "line_index": 92,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2118f71d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そんなわけないじゃん",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.0",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "87ce17c1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは我慢できなくなったように、小さく吹き出す。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "98.0",
      "line_index": 98,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bb4d88",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しばらく楽しそうに笑ったあと、コハルは{G_PlayerName}の隣へ並び、静かに窓の外を見上げた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "103.1",
      "line_index": 103,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "65a2a22d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "昔から変わらないね。あたしが近づくとすぐ意識して、目を逸らして",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "106.0",
      "line_index": 106,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a0ae8082",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "コハルがからかうからだろ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "109.1",
      "line_index": 109,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6d06649c",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "そうかもしれないけど",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.0",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9519e22",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは一度言葉を止めると、星空ではなく、隣にいる{G_PlayerName}の横顔を見つめる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "115.1",
      "line_index": 115,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "43fe0836",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "でも、こんな反応をしてくれるの、あんたしかいないから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "118.0",
      "line_index": 118,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bf3173fe",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺なら面白いのかよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "123.1",
      "line_index": 123,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a698496d",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "うん",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "125.1",
      "line_index": 125,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a8bf9440",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "それに、あんたが照れてると、あたしをちゃんと意識してるって分かるし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "128.0",
      "line_index": 128,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6d1bd97e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "なっ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "134.1",
      "line_index": 134,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "180d9c71",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "今ので三点♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "136.0",
      "line_index": 136,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "21c92a2f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "悔しそうに黙り込む{G_PlayerName}を見て、コハルは満足げに笑みを浮かべる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "138.0",
      "line_index": 138,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "529e6b12",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかし、しばらく考え込んでいた{G_PlayerName}は、今度は自分からコハルへ一歩近づいた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "145.0",
      "line_index": 145,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "81e94d06",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺もコハルを照れさせたら一点。今からルール追加、拒否権なし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.1",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d51a976a",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ちょ、ちょっと！　それは聞いてない！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8dc1ca8b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "もう始まってるから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.1",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c9cd8d4e",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "あたしの真似しないでよ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8a8b69ae",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "今日、コハルとここに来られてよかった",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "165.1",
      "line_index": 165,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b7eac30e",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……急に何よ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "168.0",
      "line_index": 168,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3ac995e1",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "星も綺麗だけど、二人で見られたから、もっと綺麗に見える",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.1",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "70b4fea7",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……っ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.0",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "672f196e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは赤くなった顔を隠すように、勢いよく窓の方へ顔を逸らした。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "180.0",
      "line_index": 180,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "58f5770f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "はい、一点。目、逸らした",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "185.1",
      "line_index": 185,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6bd75df4",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "今のなし！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "188.0",
      "line_index": 188,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7b82ad14",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "言い訳は聞きませーん",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.1",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e08389b5",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "もう……調子に乗らないでよね！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "197.0",
      "line_index": 197,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2833b3aa",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは照れを誤魔化すように、{G_PlayerName}の肩を軽く叩く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "199.0",
      "line_index": 199,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fe03e629",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかし、離れる代わりにそっと{G_PlayerName}の服の袖を掴み、そのまま肩が触れるほど近くに並んだ。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "205.0",
      "line_index": 205,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d7d555de",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "近くないか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "208.1",
      "line_index": 208,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "f345fefc",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ゲーム中だから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "211.0",
      "line_index": 211,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ee04e0ed",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "便利な言葉だな……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "216.1",
      "line_index": 216,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3a61d95f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "残り時間で、絶対あたしが勝つから",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "218.0",
      "line_index": 218,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b3e6685c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "二人は肩を寄せ合ったまま、再び窓の向こうに広がる星空を見上げる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "220.0",
      "line_index": 220,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bb968fd4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゲームを始めた時の騒がしさはなくなり、展望デッキには宇宙船の小さな駆動音だけが静かに響いていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "226.0",
      "line_index": 226,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dc7cc4a9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しばらくして、コハルが{G_PlayerName}の服の袖を掴んだまま、少しだけ恥ずかしそうに口を開く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "230.1",
      "line_index": 230,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "18d7d2e8",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "十分過ぎても、もう少しだけこのままでいてもいい？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "233.0",
      "line_index": 233,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d7945e6a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "それ、ゲームと関係あるのか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "238.1",
      "line_index": 238,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8ed979e3",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "ない",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "240.0",
      "line_index": 240,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1fea6c49",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは一度言葉を切ると、{G_PlayerName}の袖を掴む指に少しだけ力を込める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "242.1",
      "line_index": 242,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "6bd70269",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "……ずっと近くにいたいだけ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "245.0",
      "line_index": 245,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3300f9b5",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "お、おい……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "251.1",
      "line_index": 251,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d8543f4f",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "はい、四点♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "254.0",
      "line_index": 254,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6ae07a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "今のも数えるのかよ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "257.1",
      "line_index": 257,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "66753ba8",
      "speaker": "コハル",
      "ja": "もちろん。あたしの勝ちね♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "259.0",
      "line_index": 259,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "def90423",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "静かな展望デッキに、コハルの楽しそうな笑い声が響く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "261.0",
      "line_index": 261,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6d53ffeb",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "二人はゲームの終了時間を忘れ、袖をつないだまま、いつまでも星空を眺め続けた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "266.0",
      "line_index": 266,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "78b6cbc",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "コハルは、いつもこれくらい素直になる勇気が出せたらと思う。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "268.0",
      "line_index": 268,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ad1e8562",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "けれど今は、{G_PlayerName}が離れずに隣にいてくれることだけで、十分に満足しているのであった。",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
